{
  "stem": "15732.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were asked in which of the-- in which one of the displaced person camps we wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't have an idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were only names and we didn't have an idea.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They told us Foehrenwald and Landsberg and-- there were already several there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tell you how we chose.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the meantime, my father had a chat with-- with other people that were there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one of those people told him that in Foehrenwald the-- the [GERMAN], the-- the management, in the management is somehow a Jew from Tschernowitz, which is called Herman or whatever.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father decided we will- we'll got to Foehrenwald if there is somebody there from our place of the world.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think that was fate, because we arrived in-- in Foehrenwald in was probably the end of November, '45-- Where was Foehrenwald?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Foehrenwald.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Foehrenwald was not very far from Munich.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a place where most probably the Germans had some youth movement or what, because they had the houses there were for group-- rooms and one bigger room, as if they would have built that for-- for youth movement something.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We arrived in Foehrenwald.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's quite a drive out of Munich.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It is in the so-called Schwarzwald, the beautiful Black Forest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and when wed arrived there, in Foehrenwald, we again were registered, allocated a room, and allocated a number for food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This-- we were fed by the displaced person-- by UNRRA, which were the-- the relief organization.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there we started the real work to be organized, to organize one's self for Aliyah Bet, or for Israel, or contemplating starting to do something with the remnants of European Jewry.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
